b89ff56afd5e449fa391be7a96a15cb1bef3","tid":351416,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170808&amp;guid=57054739&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170808%26guid%3D57054739%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=wf4GiX5tyj8uccFk1MzqePjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=e9f08f53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170808%26guid%3D57054739%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=9fbcfd5c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170808&amp;guid=57054739&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"20ffd7fd37daafc47b40bf8be8c5601f2f90efc6","tid":351416,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ef2bae3f8d99005889b7818c93342cee246f96","tid":351416,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:30:13.000Z","msg":"一睇到係中港旅遊巴司機立即爽曬<br />\n成日渣到火箭咁"},{"pid":"146621ea2a5c4f08cb23abcc4164e2bae9771afc","tid":351416,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"玩緊手機都sense到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b12eeea225ba89097ba231a4336ffd8a1a9c92","tid":351416,"uid":65042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:30:45.000Z","msg":"走去睇下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3354a33c7037f998d48ab4ab23c465743bbf80","tid":351416,"uid":53164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:34:08.000Z","msg":"司機都冇帶安全帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc37e618fe0445744914f35b1024b2e6c5b5352d","tid":351416,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"留名睇gif"},{"pid":"84b4c57dc2d6702d2f68e0a42f1936f70acd58bc","tid":351416,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>司機都冇帶安全帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇到單新聞見到唯一死者係個飛左出去的司機<br />\n即刻屌左出聲<br />\n屌你老母做司機都唔撚戴安全帶<br />\n咩時代啦你老母"},{"pid":"e90f7b9c7e8237c419cd759d048e24293ed2c215","tid":351416,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170808/large/1502165191_3760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170808%2Flarge%2F1502165191_3760.jpg&h=c26b4f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旅遊巴司機位的安全帶右膊位有一個紅色夾，專家懷疑它是令安全帶無法箍緊司機令他飛出車外的元凶（謝志輝攝）<br />\n<br />\n新田公路旅遊巴奪命車禍中，工程師盧覺強稱從汽車受破壞程度及地面剎車痕推算，意外時時速約60至74公里，估計旅遊巴撞向平治私家車時的衝力高達11,000磅。警方正調查旅遊巴司機何以會飛出車外喪命，包括事發時司機有沒有戴安全帶、以及安全帶裝置是否有問題。據記者意外後在現場所見，旅遊巴司機位的安全帶扣已鬆開，安全帶及鎖扣部都未見損毀，惟在司機右膊位的安全帶位置卻夾著一個「紅色夾」。<br />\n<br />\n汽車工業學會會長李耀培及前理大機械工程學系工程師盧覺強同樣懷疑，該「紅色夾」極可能是職業司機常用的「安全帶固定夾」，其作用是方便司機以人手拉長安全帶後夾實它防止回彈，令安全帶較鬆動，免箍得司機胸口太緊令司機不適。但李指使用這種固定夾有機會在意外時害命，因安全帶若無法索緊司機，車禍時的直接撞擊及第二次衝擊，均可能令司機飛出車外。盧亦反對用固定夾，因使用安全帶必須要緊貼身體，撞擊時方能勒住司機，否則司機很容易被拋出座位甚至車外。"}]}